subproject.corporate outcome: Strengthened capacities of national human rights institutions
subproject.description: The project is to enhance the capacity of Central Elections Committee and Regional Elections Committee to plan, prepare and implement polling and electoral management best practices. Also, it helps increase mass media’s coverage of election process, including electoral campaigning and reporting has improved and voter awareness. Draft Unified Electoral Code is to be finalized based on contributions from various stakeholders of the electoral process and introduced to the Parliament of Turkmenistan for adoption.
subproject.title: Electoral System & Processes 2
